            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Deuteron beam of ~50 microA at 930keV bombards targets",
                "of heavy phosphoric acid (neutrons of 1.8 - 3.75 MeV)",
                "or carbon (neutrons of 0.35-0.55 MeV), mounted on a",
                "brass plate.",
                "Measurements were done at different angles relative to",
                "the deuteron beam."
              ]
            },
            {
